6:
Wow... So this is what New Year's
looks like in Yamato. Everyone's
dressed to the nines!
10:
You've got quite an ensemble going
on yourself.
14:
Hee-hee... Oh, this? I mean, it's not
every day I get to try on traditional
Yamato garb, right?
23:
Not exactly. It is a little, er, short,
don't you think?
28:
I knew it! I can't believe I let the lady
at the shop convince me it looked
fine.
32: Wait... I was scammed, wasn't I?!
38:
Now, now, let's not get carried
away—I think it looks fine on you!
41:
So what if it's a little, er, revealing,
right?
45:
Oh no... I think I'll change back to my
usual outfit after all!
51:
Huh. I thought you were in a big
hurry to try that, uh... what's it called
again?
56:
A dessert called shiruko! And you're
right—food over fashion!
59:
If we don't make it in time, we might
miss out on the event they're having
at the shop today!
69:
Welcome, welcome! 
And what can I do you fer, miss?
72: Um, one bowl of shiruko, please!
75:
One bowl of shiruko for the pretty
lady!
77:
Careful now—eat it too quickly and
you might burn yer tongue right off!
81: Ooh, I can't WAIT to dig in!
88:
Mmm... Perfect for a cold day, don't
you think?
93:
You can have the rest of mine. This
sugary-sweet stuff ain't for me.
97:
Really? That's the best part—the
perfect harmony of sweet bean
goodness and chewy mochi is to die
for!
100:
Hah! This little missy gets it. In fact,
you'd be a perfect contender for our
annual shiruko eatin' contest!
102:
If you win, everything's on the house!
You'll also get a chance to try our
deluxe, limited-time-only New Year's
shiruko with all the works!
106:
With all... the works? 
Ooough, I... I want it!
109:
But I don't know how I'd feel about
entering something like this all by
myself...
114:
Hey, don't look at me—I couldn't
even put my own bowl away.
119:
Regrettably, I can only consume so
much in my current form.
123:
I'll give it a shot. Plus, I'm dying to
know what's in their New Year's
shiruko.
130: I, too, would like to participate.
136:
Really? Thank you, thank you! Let's
win this thing!
139:
Come one, come, all! It's time for our
annual shiruko extravaganza!
Eaters, are you ready?
141: On your mark, get set... mochi!
146: Ngh... I think I've reached my limit...
151: Oof... Same... I'm about to burst...
156:
I cannot... go on. Rebecca, please
complete the remainder of our
objective.
161:
O-okay! I think I have room for a
little more!
165: H-HEY! Now's not a good time!
168:
What are you—wait, you want some
too?
171:
N-no, you can't! That'd be against
the rules! No shadows allowed!
177:
Is she employing help from her
shadows?
187:
I-I'm not doing it on purpose, you
guys! I just... I can't get them under
control!
190:
And two more contestants have
thrown in the towel, ladies and
gents! That leaves... the lovely miss
Rebecca as your shiruko superstar!
198:
What's that, missy? Cheating?
Shadow magic?
203:
I'm so sorry! I didn't mean for this to
happen—sometimes they just come
out like this, and, well…
206:
Eh. As long it wasn't on purpose,
right? No harm, no foul. In fact, this
might give our shop the boost it's
been lookin' for!
210:
Is that supposed to be... Rebecca's
face?
218:
Whatcha think of it? We're gonna
leave this up all year until next year's
contest!
223:
You mean this is going to be here...
for an entire year?! I wasn't told
about any of this!
226:
I-I never asked to be a... a shiruko
shogun!
